{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.1","label":"","reference":"Juges 17:1","prev_osis_id":"Judg.016.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.017.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Culte dans la maison de Mica en \u00c9phra\u00efm; le jeune L\u00e9vite au service de Mica<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-13: cf. De 27:15. Jg 8:24-27. J\u00e9 50:6. Pr 14:12.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.17.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Il y avait un homme de la montagne d\u2019\u00c9phra\u00efm, nomm\u00e9 Mica.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.17","name":"Juges 17","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.17.2","name":"Juges 17:2","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.16.31","name":"Juges 16:31","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.16.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.2","label":"","reference":"Juges 17:2","prev_osis_id":"Judg.017.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.017.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.17.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Il dit \u00e0 sa m\u00e8re: Les mille et cent sicles d\u2019argent qu\u2019on t\u2019a pris, et pour lesquels tu as fait des impr\u00e9cations m\u00eame \u00e0 mes oreilles, voici, cet argent est entre mes mains, c\u2019est moi qui l\u2019avais pris. Et sa m\u00e8re dit: B\u00e9ni soit mon fils par l\u2019\u00c9ternel!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.17","name":"Juges 17","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.17.3","name":"Juges 17:3","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.17.1","name":"Juges 17:1","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.3","label":"","reference":"Juges 17:3","prev_osis_id":"Judg.017.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.017.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.17.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Il rendit \u00e0 sa m\u00e8re les mille et cent sicles d\u2019argent; et sa m\u00e8re dit: Je consacre de ma main cet argent \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, afin d\u2019en faire pour mon fils une image taill\u00e9e et une image en fonte; et c\u2019est ainsi que je te le rendrai.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.17","name":"Juges 17","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.17.4","name":"Juges 17:4","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.17.2","name":"Juges 17:2","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.4","label":"","reference":"Juges 17:4","prev_osis_id":"Judg.017.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.017.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.17.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Il rendit \u00e0 sa m\u00e8re l\u2019argent. Sa m\u00e8re prit deux cents sicles d\u2019argent. Et elle donna l\u2019argent au fondeur, qui en fit une image taill\u00e9e et une image en fonte. On les pla\u00e7a dans la maison de Mica.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.17","name":"Juges 17","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.17.5","name":"Juges 17:5","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.17.3","name":"Juges 17:3","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.5","label":"","reference":"Juges 17:5","prev_osis_id":"Judg.017.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.017.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.17.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Ce Mica avait une maison de Dieu; il fit un \u00e9phod et des th\u00e9raphim, et il consacra l\u2019un de ses fils, qui lui servit de pr\u00eatre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.17","name":"Juges 17","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.17.6","name":"Juges 17:6","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.17.4","name":"Juges 17:4","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.6","label":"","reference":"Juges 17:6","prev_osis_id":"Judg.017.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.017.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.17.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>En ce temps-l\u00e0, il n\u2019y avait point de roi en Isra\u00ebl. Chacun faisait ce qui lui semblait bon.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.17","name":"Juges 17","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.17.7","name":"Juges 17:7","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.17.5","name":"Juges 17:5","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.7","label":"","reference":"Juges 17:7","prev_osis_id":"Judg.017.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.017.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.17.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Il y avait un jeune homme de Bethl\u00e9hem de Juda, de la famille de Juda; il \u00e9tait L\u00e9vite, et il s\u00e9journait l\u00e0.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.17","name":"Juges 17","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.17.8","name":"Juges 17:8","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.17.6","name":"Juges 17:6","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.8","label":"","reference":"Juges 17:8","prev_osis_id":"Judg.017.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.017.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.17.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Cet homme partit de la ville de Bethl\u00e9hem de Juda, pour chercher une demeure qui lui conv\u00eent. En poursuivant son chemin, il arriva dans la montagne d\u2019\u00c9phra\u00efm jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la maison de Mica.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.17","name":"Juges 17","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.17.9","name":"Juges 17:9","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.17.7","name":"Juges 17:7","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.9","label":"","reference":"Juges 17:9","prev_osis_id":"Judg.017.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.017.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.17.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Mica lui dit: D\u2019o\u00f9 viens-tu? Il lui r\u00e9pondit: Je suis L\u00e9vite, de Bethl\u00e9hem de Juda, et je voyage pour chercher une demeure qui me convienne.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.17","name":"Juges 17","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.17.10","name":"Juges 17:10","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.17.8","name":"Juges 17:8","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.10","label":"","reference":"Juges 17:10","prev_osis_id":"Judg.017.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.017.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.17.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Mica lui dit: Reste avec moi; tu me serviras de p\u00e8re et de pr\u00eatre, et je te donnerai dix sicles d\u2019argent par ann\u00e9e, les v\u00eatements dont tu auras besoin, et ton entretien. Et le L\u00e9vite entra.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.17","name":"Juges 17","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.17.11","name":"Juges 17:11","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.17.9","name":"Juges 17:9","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.11","label":"","reference":"Juges 17:11","prev_osis_id":"Judg.017.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.017.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.17.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Il se d\u00e9cida ainsi \u00e0 rester avec cet homme, qui regarda le jeune homme comme l\u2019un de ses fils.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.17","name":"Juges 17","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.17.12","name":"Juges 17:12","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.17.10","name":"Juges 17:10","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.12","label":"","reference":"Juges 17:12","prev_osis_id":"Judg.017.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.017.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.17.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Mica consacra le L\u00e9vite, et ce jeune homme lui servit de pr\u00eatre et demeura dans sa maison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.17","name":"Juges 17","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.17.13","name":"Juges 17:13","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.17.11","name":"Juges 17:11","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.13","label":"","reference":"Juges 17:13","prev_osis_id":"Judg.017.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.018.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.17.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Et Mica dit: Maintenant, je sais que l\u2019\u00c9ternel me fera du bien, puisque j\u2019ai ce L\u00e9vite pour pr\u00eatre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.17","name":"Juges 17","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.18.1","name":"Juges 18:1","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.18.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.17.12","name":"Juges 17:12","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.17.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb1e2f031.31073495');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb1e2f031.31073495\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb1e2f031.31073495","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb1e2f031.31073495'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb1e2f031.31073495\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}